{"tid":1442054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究 竟 幾 時 先 完","createTime":"2019-08-10T21:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T21:24:03.000Z","uid":303983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd6fd39e6c6a1fe0e469d23e242c920da4d0d78","tid":1442054,"uid":303983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:05:43.000Z","msg":"近排晚晚都係到諗，呢場公民抗命會幾時完，點樣完。會持續半年呢種生活，抑或係一年，甚至係幾年呢？<br />\n到最後係林鄭落台完左呢件事，定係會發生一件無人估到既事，然後結束左呢場運動呢<br />\n<br />\n無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但</span>我知既係，我地無路可退，我地一定同個八婆，同啲高官，同啲狗察鬥長命！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日見！</span><br />\n<br />\n利申 第一次開post 唔識用"},{"pid":"d121f351378cb37733c644181efd7845397e12e4","tid":1442054,"uid":145314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:08:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭一日唔落台都好難服眾"},{"pid":"39372b97fa6fb353bb88c559c6e4b846ea637419","tid":1442054,"uid":303983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d121f351378cb37733c644181efd7845397e12e4","tid":1442054,"uid":145314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:08:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭一日唔落台都好難服眾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:09:52.000Z","msg":"其實邊個做都係一樣，不過呢個仆街係仆街之中既仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb15ff3f79d0b1b5fdb573362648a95f01555ada","tid":1442054,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:10:07.000Z","msg":"[長文] 大家睇下咁樣會唔會係走出第五階段嘅新方向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442009</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁樣有無得完？"},{"pid":"07a0adf0e2ba83e72c04ca632bf7ccfd72068b61","tid":1442054,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislik